      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王伯谷上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00002",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "小工调步步娇",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "甚风儿吹得我心摇扬，辗转增惆怅。酒力助诗狂，撩乱情怀好难安放。（白）小生王伯谷，京江人士。春闱落第，流寓京师，赋性不羁，放怀诗酒。只为功名失意，却教花柳情牵。物色多时，才访得姑苏马湘兰。见她姿容秀美，吐属温柔，常与往来。可笑近日都中有一种风气，凡有名的姊儿不拘好歹，都要画几笔兰花。哈哈，这是小生的专门。因此将笔法传授湘兰。且喜她生就聪明，不多几日，功夫早已名重一时了。今日独酌无聊𠮩，不免去寻她作画一回，以遣酒性便了。（小工调步步娇）扶醉过平康，为丹青特地把红裙访。（白）来此已是兰娘门首。吓开门！",
      "text_length": 250
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00003",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小环上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00004",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小环"
      ],
      "text": "来了！（念）忽听叩门声，知是佳客至。（白）是哪个？原来是王相公。请客堂坐。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00005",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "兰娘在家否？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00006",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小环"
      ],
      "text": "在里面。相公请坐，待我唤她。吓，湘娘，王相公来了！快些出来吓！",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00007",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "来了！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00008",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "马湘兰上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00009",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "风马儿",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "偷闲读画坐文窗，闻小婢唤檀郎。（白）相公万福！王伯谷（白）湘娘拜揖。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00010",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "请坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00011",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "有坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00012",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "今日甚风吹得到此？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00013",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "独酌无聊，故而到此。不知湘娘作何消遣？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00014",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "就是相公前日醉后画的那幅墨兰，奴家爱玩不止，在里面临摹一回。（风马儿）深惭婢学夫人样，恰自调水墨亲手写三湘。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00015",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "哈哈！小生正为看画而来。当面请教如何？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00016",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "只是临的不好，不要见笑。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00017",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "自然是好的！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00018",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王伯谷看。众妓女持画同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
