    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00052",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄莺儿",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00053",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白王伯谷",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00054",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00055",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "集贤宾翰墨久名扬，怪妖娆忒擅长，特来比较谁能让。姐姐妹妹我们都是京内有名的粉头，多会画几笔兰花。不多京内无双，就是进贡都可进得。不想马湘兰相与了个穷酸，教他几笔虾米炒韭的兰花来欺侮我们。为此我们用心画了几幅，前来与她比较。这里是了门儿开在此。吓妹，子几日不见，更标致了。众位姐姐请坐。原来在此看画。此位是？这就是王相公了。哦，这就是会画兰花的么？吓王相公，你是有名的大才子！岂敢！吓为什么拿了虾米炒韭菜似的兰花在这里赞赏？我们带了几幅兰花，在此倒要请教。这是妙极的雅事！取来。哈哈，这亦是兰花𠮾哟，可不辱没煞兰花！可好？好好好！不是我们夸口，就是相公也未必画得出来哟！你自去端详自去思量，相公你随我去。放手，放手！嗳，好惹厌！啐！难道奴妆台没个人相偎傍，太猖狂，花花叶叶相对复相当。我们不要理这酸生，走罢！我的酒多被她们闹醒了。何不再饮几杯？使得。小环，看酒来！来了！酒在此，王相公请用酒。湘娘，你自作画，待我饮酒赏画便了。小环，取文房四宝与冰绡一幅。是。文具冰绡在此。取来。啧啧啧，好一幅叠雪香罗与鸾笺一样。待我把敬一杯。待我自斟自饮。湘娘就请动笔如何？如此献丑了。拈银毫纤纤玉笋长，看春风摇曳花笺上。觑着他酒态淋漓，这笔墨里添得些风流倜傥，你看我淡写轻描，可抵得过浅斟低唱，早出现一枝空谷幽香。相公请看阿呀妙吓！羡煞她比沾墨妙真擅长，恰天然满纸芬芳。借酒气将花来酝酿，引得她返香魂当天仙供养。（白）不知闺中笔墨，怎能佳妙至此？????，我晓得了！（集贤宾）这就是名花色相，这就是佳人图样，分明是自家写出绝代红妆。",
      "text_length": 658
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00056",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "既蒙见举，就请相公一题。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00057",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "只怕我醉后题诗不好。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00058",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "哎相公吓！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00059",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "啼莺儿你才人镇日在诗酒场，酒狂不碍诗狂。只要你一字留题，也免得我孤芳自赏，写乌丝字两行。绝妙好辞安排佳酿，润诗肠。王伯谷",
      "text_length": 60
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00060",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "写完了，请看。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00061",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "“自拂花笺字写真，如花人作画花人。东风多少闲桃李，不及幽闺一剪香。”好蕴藉风流的是才子之笔。奴家若非相公朝夕指教，也不过似她们一样辱没兰花。相公请上，待奴一拜！",
      "text_length": 80
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00062",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "阿呀阿呀，何须如此！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00063",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "黄莺儿",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "亏得我金钗作贽侥幸败门墙。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00064",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "今日这等雅集，合城中也不多得。取大杯来，与你痛饮一回。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00065",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "小环，取热酒来。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00066",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小环"
      ],
      "text": "是。王相公，你已醉了，何苦还要喝它？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00067",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "你哪里知道这醉乡滋味哟！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00068",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "小环"
      ],
      "text": "不过醉倒街头。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00069",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "好没规矩。下去！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00070",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "小环下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00071",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "马湘兰"
      ],
      "text": "相公请！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00072",
      "play_id": "13003008",
      "scene_id": "13003008_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王伯谷"
      ],
      "text": "请！干！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "13003008_e00073",
